title: PC Format Magazine June 2014
description:
PC Format Magazine June 2014
 English | 100 Pages | True PDF | 26MB


PC Format is a computer magazine published in the United Kingdom by Future plc, and licensed to other publishers in countries around the world. In publication since 1991, it is part of Future plc's Format series of magazines that include articles about games, entertainment and how to get the most out of the platform. Despite the occasional mention of alternatives, PC Format takes the term 'PC' to mean a Microsoft Windows-based computer
